<h1 >5.2.3.30 Widow B, C &amp; D Pension, Bereavement Allowance - July 1942 to Present Date</h1>
<h2><a href="../guide-social-security-law/acronyms#widb" title="Widow B pension">WidB</a> (also class D from 24 June 1947 to 28 February 1961 <a href="16048#NoteA">Note A</a>)</h2>
<p>The following table shows the <a href="../guide-social-security-law/acronyms#mbr" title="Maximum basic rate">MBR</a> of WidB in dollars per annum. The MBR of <a href="../guide-social-security-law/acronyms#bva" title="Bereavement allowance">BVA</a> is the same as that of WidB. For rates of supplementary payments linked to WidB or BVA, see <a href="../guide-social-security-law/5/2/2/05">5.2.2.05</a>.</p>
